### 1. 배송 등록 (Create Delivery)
POST http://localhost:8080/deliveries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceNumber": "TEST123456",
  "status": "PREPARING"
}

###

### 2. 배송 단건 조회 (Get Delivery)
GET http://localhost:8080/deliveries/TEST123456
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. 배송 상태 변경 - PREPARING → SHIPPED
PUT http://localhost:8080/deliveries/TEST123456/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newStatus": "SHIPPED"
}

###

### 4. 상태 변경 후 도착예정일 확인
GET http://localhost:8080/deliveries/TEST123456
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. 유효하지 않은 상태 변경 (SHIPPED → PREPARING 불가능)
PUT http://localhost:8080/deliveries/TEST123456/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newStatus": "PREPARING"
}

###

### 6. 존재하지 않는 송장 조회 (예외 처리 확인)
GET http://localhost:8080/deliveries/NOT_EXIST
Accept: application/json